snippet.title: Johnny Depp Thanks His Fans For Getting a MASSIVE Win Over Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Welcome back to our channel, Fabulously Famous. The topic that will be discussed today is  Johnny Depp Thanks His Fans For Getting a MASSIVE Win Over Amber Heard. But before we start, subscribe to our channel and don't miss any updates!

Johnny Depp paused for a minute to thank his allies on Friday in the midst of information his $50 million slander preliminary against ex Amber Heard will be pushed back due to Covid concerns.

He shared a video of himself in a work area before an enormous, loaded cabinet as he worked out a thank-you letter. Johnny reiterated the content of his note in the inscription, which read: "Hi All! I simply needed to thank you all by and by for your consistent, and steadfast help all through many long, and intriguing scenes of my life… I am just here as a result of you — and I'm just here for you!!!" 

Musician, author, and dissident Patti Smith was among the many fans who answered to the star, remarking, "As the Libertine said: Ink not drink. Watching you compose fills me with joy. We as a whole love you generally."

Johnny's appreciative energies could be identified with the news his body of evidence against his ex has been rescheduled from January to May.
